{
  "texts": [
    "• RQ4: Will adopting different loss functions mitigate the class-imbalance problem thus improve the performance?",
    "To address those research questions, we design our experiments as follows:",
    "• Cross-domain experiments denote the case where existing datasets of stance towards claims are exploited for training.",
    "Each of the stance datasets is first used solely for training our models, then all datasets were aggregated and used for training.",
    "We refer to the datasets of stance towards claims as cross-domain datasets in the rest of the paper."
  ]
}